parameters: \n<Ameria>"Yes, that should do it! But please rest for a while."
\n<Abel's refugee a>"Ah... I feel so much better! Thank you, Ameria-chan."

\n<Ameria>"Next, please! --Mhm... Mhm... It's okay, you'll feel better
soon! I'm going to start the treatment now, so please stay
still for a bit."
\n<Abel's refugee a>"Yeah, it's definitely better than medicine!"

\n<Abel's refugee a>"Really, I'm glad Ameria-chan is here. When I heard Luerre-
san wouldn't be back for a while, I wondered what we'd do,
but with Ameria-chan here, I feel relieved."

\n<Abel's refugee c>"Yeah. But when will the guards come back? They just up and
left the village suddenly. If it stays like this, it'll
still be dangerous to return to the village..."

\n<Abel's refugee b>"Hmm... Maybe we'll have to consider moving to Annabern
permanently."
\n<Abel's refugee c>"Yes, thank you. You've been a lifesaver!"

\n<Refugee a from another village>"Hey, hey! Can we switch turns? A monster injured my leg and
I can't walk, please...!"

\n<Refugee c from another village>"Wait, then we should be first! We evacuated here before
they did!"

\n<Ameria>"Calm down! I'll make sure to see everyone, in order! In
order!"

\n<Lyric>"As you can see, it's very busy. There don't seem to be many
with serious injuries, but it might take quite some time to
see everyone. How about you?"

\n<Roselitte>"It seems certain that there is a band of thieves around
Anatose.... Whether they are our trading partners is unclear
though."

\n<Roselitte>"The thieves seem to have made their home in the forest
beyond Abel. We might be able to get some information, so
although it's a detour, let's go through Abel on our way to
Anatose."

\n<Lyric>"Understood. Head towards Abel and if we find any clues,
we'll go to the thieves' hideout. If not, we'll continue
straight to Anatose."

\n<Lyric>"...So, are we departing now? It seems Ameria will still
need some time."

\n<Roselitte>"Indeed... There seem to be more injured people than I
imagined, so let's wait a little longer.... Besides--"

\n<Abel's refugee c>"Thank you... Thanks to Ameria-chan, everyone is being
saved."

\n<Abel's refugee c>"Truly, she's like an angel to us. This might also be some
kind of divine providence.... Hallelujah."

\n<Roselitte>"...Seeing her so lively like that. Let's allow her to
continue her work as a healer for a bit longer."
